metadata.name: Neybors NFT
metadata.description: This NFT commemorates Heno.'s record, NEYBORS, surpassing more than one million streams on DSPs after selling out as a Web3 native release. As a token of his appreciation, Heno. made this limited edition NFT exclusive to the original holders of the song NEYBORS on Soundxyz.  Thank y'all for the continued support!!
